WASH FAMILY ENTERPRISES, INC. d/b/a Wash Family Construction, Inc., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
L. Martin HURBI and Threse Quinnhurbi, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3836 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 25, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's petition for writ of prohibition is denied. Petitioner's request for oral argument is denied as moot.

KELLY, CRENSHAW, and LUCAS, JJ., Concur.
